   "source": [
    "# 2.5 强化学习 (Reinforcement Learning)\n",
    "\n",
    "智能体通过与环境交互获得奖励信号，学习最大化累积奖励的策略。强化学习是RLHF对齐训练的理论基础。\n",
    "\n",
    "本节涵盖：\n",
    "- 策略梯度（REINFORCE）\n",
    "- PPO\n",
    "- RLHF\n",
    "- 自我博弈强化学习\n",
    "- 离线强化学习"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 策略梯度（REINFORCE）\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：直接优化策略函数\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：直接参数化策略π(a|s)，通过采样轨迹估计策略梯度，沿梯度方向更新策略参数使高奖励动作的概率增大。\n",
    "\n",
    "核心公式：∇J(θ) = E[∇log π(a|s) · R]\n",
    "\n",
    "其中R是累积奖励。直觉：如果某条轨迹获得了高奖励，就增大产生该轨迹的动作概率。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class PolicyNetwork(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, state_dim=4, action_dim=3):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.net = nn.Sequential(\n",
    "            nn.Linear(state_dim, 64), nn.ReLU(),\n",
    "            nn.Linear(64, action_dim)\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return F.softmax(self.net(x), dim=-1)\n",
    "\n",
    "policy = PolicyNetwork()\n",
    "optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(policy.parameters(), lr=1e-3)\n",
    "\n",
    "def simulate_environment(state, action):\n",
    "    reward = (state * (action + 1)).sum().item() / state.size(0)\n",
    "    next_state = state + torch.randn_like(state) * 0.1\n",
    "    return next_state, reward\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== REINFORCE Policy Gradient ===')\n",
    "reward_history = []\n",
    "for episode in range(100):\n",
    "    state = torch.randn(1, 4)\n",
    "    log_probs, rewards = [], []\n",
    "    for step in range(10):\n",
    "        probs = policy(state)\n",
    "        dist = torch.distributions.Categorical(probs)\n",
    "        action = dist.sample()\n",
    "        log_prob = dist.log_prob(action)\n",
    "        next_state, reward = simulate_environment(state, action)\n",
    "        log_probs.append(log_prob)\n",
    "        rewards.append(reward)\n",
    "        state = next_state\n",
    "\n",
    "    returns = []\n",
    "    G = 0\n",
    "    for r in reversed(rewards):\n",
    "        G = r + 0.99 * G\n",
    "        returns.insert(0, G)\n",
    "    returns = torch.tensor(returns)\n",
    "    returns = (returns - returns.mean()) / (returns.std() + 1e-8)\n",
    "\n",
    "    policy_loss = sum(-lp * G for lp, G in zip(log_probs, returns))\n",
    "    optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "    policy_loss.backward()\n",
    "    optimizer.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "    avg_reward = sum(rewards) / len(rewards)\n",
    "    reward_history.append(avg_reward)\n",
    "    if (episode + 1) % 25 == 0:\n",
    "        print(f'Episode {episode+1}: avg_reward={avg_reward:.3f}, loss={policy_loss.item():.3f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'\\nReward trend: early={sum(reward_history[:10])/10:.3f} -> late={sum(reward_history[-10:])/10:.3f}')\n",
    "print('Key: REINFORCE uses log_prob * reward to increase probability of high-reward actions.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. PPO（Proximal Policy Optimization）\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：稳定地优化语言模型策略\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：PPO通过裁剪目标函数限制每次策略更新的幅度，避免更新过大导致性能崩溃。同时使用KL散度惩罚约束策略不偏离参考模型过远。\n",
    "\n",
    "核心公式：L_CLIP = E[min(r(θ)·A, clip(r(θ), 1-ε, 1+ε)·A)]\n",
    "\n",
    "其中r(θ) = π_new(a|s) / π_old(a|s)是策略比率，A是优势函数，ε是裁剪参数（通常0.2）。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class SimplePolicy(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, dim=16, n_actions=4):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.net = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(dim, 32), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(32, n_actions))\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.net(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "policy = SimplePolicy()\n",
    "ref_policy = SimplePolicy()\n",
    "ref_policy.load_state_dict(policy.state_dict())\n",
    "ref_policy.eval()\n",
    "optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(policy.parameters(), lr=3e-4)\n",
    "\n",
    "def compute_ppo_loss(old_logp, new_logp, advantages, clip_eps=0.2):\n",
    "    ratio = torch.exp(new_logp - old_logp)\n",
    "    surr1 = ratio * advantages\n",
    "    surr2 = torch.clamp(ratio, 1 - clip_eps, 1 + clip_eps) * advantages\n",
    "    return -torch.min(surr1, surr2).mean()\n",
    "\n",
    "def compute_kl_penalty(new_logits, ref_logits, beta=0.01):\n",
    "    new_p = F.log_softmax(new_logits, dim=-1)\n",
    "    ref_p = F.log_softmax(ref_logits, dim=-1)\n",
    "    kl = (F.softmax(new_p, dim=-1) * (new_p - ref_p)).sum(dim=-1).mean()\n",
    "    return beta * kl\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== PPO Training Demo ===')\n",
    "dim, n_actions, batch_size = 16, 4, 64\n",
    "\n",
    "for update in range(50):\n",
    "    states = torch.randn(batch_size, dim)\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        old_logits = policy(states)\n",
    "        old_logp = F.log_softmax(old_logits, dim=-1)\n",
    "        actions = torch.randint(0, n_actions, (batch_size,))\n",
    "        old_action_logp = old_logp.gather(1, actions.unsqueeze(1)).squeeze(1)\n",
    "        advantages = torch.randn(batch_size)\n",
    "\n",
    "    for _ in range(4):\n",
    "        new_logits = policy(states)\n",
    "        new_logp = F.log_softmax(new_logits, dim=-1)\n",
    "        new_action_logp = new_logp.gather(1, actions.unsqueeze(1)).squeeze(1)\n",
    "        with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "            ref_logits = ref_policy(states)\n",
    "\n",
    "        ppo_loss = compute_ppo_loss(old_action_logp, new_action_logp, advantages)\n",
    "        kl_loss = compute_kl_penalty(new_logits, ref_logits)\n",
    "        total_loss = ppo_loss + kl_loss\n",
    "\n",
    "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "        total_loss.backward()\n",
    "        optimizer.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "    if (update + 1) % 10 == 0:\n",
    "        with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "            ratio = torch.exp(new_action_logp - old_action_logp)\n",
    "            print(f'Update {update+1}: ppo_loss={ppo_loss.item():.4f}, kl={kl_loss.item():.4f}, ratio_mean={ratio.mean():.3f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print('\\nKey: PPO clips the policy ratio to prevent too-large updates.')\n",
    "print('This is the core algorithm used in RLHF for LLMs.')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
