   "source": [
    "## 4. 自我博弈强化学习\n",
    "\n",
    "**目的**：通过自我对弈不断提升策略水平\n",
    "\n",
    "**基本原理**：让模型同时扮演生成者和评判者，通过多轮自我博弈不断优化策略，类似AlphaGo的自我对弈机制。代表方法：SPIN（Self-Play Fine-Tuning）。\n",
    "\n",
    "SPIN方法：\n",
    "1. 用当前模型生成回复\n",
    "2. 将生成的回复作为\"负样本\"，人类数据作为\"正样本\"\n",
    "3. 训练模型区分两者\n",
    "4. 随着模型提升，生成越来越接近人类数据的回复"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import copy\n",
    "\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "class SelfPlayAgent(nn.Module):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, dim=16):\n",
    "        super().__init__()\n",
    "        self.net = nn.Sequential(nn.Linear(dim, 32), nn.ReLU(), nn.Linear(32, 1))\n",
    "    def forward(self, x):\n",
    "        return self.net(x).squeeze(-1)\n",
    "\n",
    "current_agent = SelfPlayAgent()\n",
    "optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(current_agent.parameters(), lr=1e-3)\n",
    "\n",
    "human_data = torch.randn(100, 16) + 1.0\n",
    "\n",
    "print('=== Self-Play Fine-Tuning (SPIN-style) ===')\n",
    "for round_num in range(5):\n",
    "    prev_agent = copy.deepcopy(current_agent)\n",
    "    prev_agent.eval()\n",
    "\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        noise_scale = max(0.1, 1.0 - round_num * 0.2)\n",
    "        generated = human_data + torch.randn_like(human_data) * noise_scale\n",
    "\n",
    "    human_scores = current_agent(human_data)\n",
    "    gen_scores = current_agent(generated)\n",
    "    loss = -torch.log(torch.sigmoid(human_scores - gen_scores)).mean()\n",
    "\n",
    "    optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "    loss.backward()\n",
    "    optimizer.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():\n",
    "        accuracy = (human_scores > gen_scores).float().mean()\n",
    "        score_gap = (human_scores - gen_scores).mean()\n",
    "    print(f'Round {round_num+1}: loss={loss.item():.4f}, accuracy={accuracy:.3f}, score_gap={score_gap:.3f}, noise={noise_scale:.2f}')\n",
    "\n",
    "print('\\nKey: Each round, the agent learns to distinguish human data from its own generations.')\n",
    "print('As noise decreases, generated data becomes harder to distinguish -> agent improves.')"
   ]
  },
  {
